    {
      "type": "warmup",
      "content": "<h2>Warm-up (2-3 min)</h2>\n<p>Yesterday&#39;s vocabulary:</p>\n<pre><code>day → ?      month → ?\nweek → ?     year → ?\n</code></pre>\n<p>(Answers: <code>djedi</code>, <code>masti</code>, <code>jeftu</code>, <code>nanca</code>)</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "material",
      "content": "<h2>New Material (5-7 min)</h2>\n<h3>New Vocabulary</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Lojban</th>\n<th>Place Structure</th>\n<th>English</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>cerni</code></td>\n<td>x1 is morning of day x2 at location x3</td>\n<td>morning</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>vanci</code></td>\n<td>x1 is evening of day x2 at location x3</td>\n<td>evening</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>nicte</code></td>\n<td>x1 is night of day x2 at location x3</td>\n<td>night</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>temci</code></td>\n<td>x1 is a time/duration</td>\n<td>time</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>detri</code></td>\n<td>x1 is the date of event x2 at location x3</td>\n<td>date</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Day Parts</h3>\n<pre><code>ca cerni\n</code></pre>\n<p>It is morning now. (Now is morning.)</p>\n<pre><code>ti vanci\n</code></pre>\n<p>This is evening.</p>\n<pre><code>mi sipna ca lo nicte\n</code></pre>\n<p>I sleep during the night.</p>\n<h3>Time and Date</h3>\n<pre><code>ma temci\n</code></pre>\n<p>What time is it?</p>\n<pre><code>ma detri\n</code></pre>\n<p>What is the date?</p>\n<h3>Combining with Actions</h3>\n<pre><code>mi citka ca lo cerni\n</code></pre>\n<p>I eat during the morning. (I eat breakfast.)</p>\n<pre><code>mi gunka ca lo vanci\n</code></pre>\n<p>I work during the evening.</p>\n<h3>Key Point</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>cerni</code>, <code>vanci</code>, <code>nicte</code> name parts of the day. <code>temci</code> and <code>detri</code> refer to time and dates.</p>\n</blockquote>\n",
      "title": "New Material (5-7 min)"
    },
