      "type": "practice",
      "content": "<h2>Practice (4-5 min)</h2>\n<h3>Exercise 1: Day Part Sentences</h3>\n<p>Translate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>It is morning.</li>\n<li>This is night.</li>\n<li>I like evening.</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>ca cerni</code> or <code>ti cerni</code></li>\n<li><code>ti nicte</code></li>\n<li><code>mi nelci lo vanci</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Exercise 2: Activities by Day Part</h3>\n<p>Translate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I eat in the morning.</li>\n<li>I work in the evening.</li>\n<li>I sleep at night.</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>mi citka ca lo cerni</code></li>\n<li><code>mi gunka ca lo vanci</code></li>\n<li><code>mi sipna ca lo nicte</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Exercise 3: Time Questions</h3>\n<p>Translate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>What time is it?</li>\n<li>What is the date?</li>\n<li>The time is short.</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>ma temci</code></li>\n<li><code>ma detri</code></li>\n<li><code>lo temci cu tordu</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>",
